      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Grasp the Gunlance",
        "Client": "Master Utsushi",
        "Description": "Alright, Ace, lesson time!\r\nGetting in your target\u0027s face\r\nand remaining calm is the key\r\nto unleashing the true potential\r\nof the gunlance. And no monster\r\nteaches \u0022in-your-face\u0022 better\r\nthan the \u003CCOL RED\u003EBarioth\u003C/COL\u003E!",
        "Target": "Capture a Barioth",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, time expires,\r\nor capture target slain"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "D\u00E9couverte du lancecanon",
        "Client": "Utsushi le ma\u00EEtre",
        "Description": "Bon, je t\u0027explique ! Avoir sa cible\r\nbien en vue et garder son calme,\r\nc\u0027est la cl\u00E9 avec le lancecanon\r\nEt s\u0027il y a un bien monstre qui\r\nsait encadrer sa cible, c\u0027est\r\nle \u003CCOL RED\u003EBarioth\u003C/COL\u003E. Prends-en de la graine !",
        "Target": "Capturer un Barioth",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9\r\nCible tu\u00E9e"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Apprendi la lancia-fucile",
        "Client": "Maestro Utsushi",
        "Description": "OK, \u00E8 ora di imparare: per\r\nsfruttare il potenziale della\r\nlancia-fucile, la chiave \u00E8\r\ntrovarsi dinanzi al bersaglio\r\ne rimanere calmi. E non c\u0027\u00E8\r\nnulla di meglio di un \u003CCOL RED\u003EBarioth\u003C/COL\u003E\r\nper apprendere questa tecnica!",
        "Target": "Cattura un Barioth",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero, tempo scaduto\r\no mostro da catturare ucciso"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Grundlagen der Gewehrlanze",
        "Client": "Meister Utsushi",
        "Description": "Okay, Ass, aufgepasst! Nase an\r\nNase mit dem Ziel zu sein und\r\ndabei ruhig zu bleiben, ist der\r\nSchl\u00FCssel zum Meistern der\r\nGewehrlanze. Und wenn dir ein\r\nMonster brutal die Nase brechen\r\nwill, ist es der \u003CCOL RED\u003EBarioth\u003C/COL\u003E!",
        "Target": "Fange einen Barioth.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0, Zeit l\u00E4uft ab\r\noder Fangziel erlegt."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Domina la lanza pistola",
        "Client": "Maestro Utsushi",
        "Description": "Hacha, \u00A1hora de aprender!\r\nDesatar el verdadero potencial\r\nde la lanza pistola requiere\r\nuna ejecuci\u00F3n s\u00F3lida. El\r\nestilo recio del \u003CCOL RED\u003EBarioth\u003C/COL\u003E es lo\r\nque buscas. \u00A1Captura uno y\r\nest\u00FAdialo bien!",
